        "created_by": "elastic",
        "description": "Find MCP configuration files on Windows endpoints. Use for shadow AI discovery — scans well-known user profile paths for Claude Desktop, Cursor, and VS Code MCP configuration files that define which MCP servers are permitted to run, revealing AI tool deployments and integrations.",
